---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use | Growth Room"
  description="Terms of Use for Growth Room — rules and conditions for using our website and purchasing our online courses."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] text-zinc-300">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20 sm:px-8">

      <a href="/" class="mb-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-[#C9A44A] transition">
        ← Back to Growth Room
      </a>

      <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
        Terms of Use
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-500">Last updated: June 4, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using the Growth Room website (<strong class="text-zinc-200">growthroom.co</strong>) or purchasing any
            product or course through <strong class="text-zinc-200">afilma.com</strong>, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use.
            If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">2. Description of Services</h2>
          <p>
            Growth Room offers digital products including, but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>Online courses and video lessons on paid advertising and digital marketing.</li>
            <li>Weekly live coaching and mastermind sessions.</li>
            <li>Templates, frameworks, and downloadable resources.</li>
            <li>Access to a private community of practitioners.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            All digital products are sold and delivered via the <strong class="text-zinc-200">afilma.com</strong> platform.
            Purchasing is subject to afilma.com's own terms and conditions in addition to these Terms of Use.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">3. Eligibility</h2>
          <p>
            You must be at least 18 years old to purchase our products or use our services. By making a
            purchase, you represent that you meet this age requirement and have the legal capacity to enter
            into a binding agreement.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">4. Purchases and Payment</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>All prices are listed in US Dollars (USD) or Brazilian Reais (BRL) as shown at checkout and are inclusive of applicable taxes unless stated otherwise.</li>
            <li>Payment is processed securely through <strong class="text-zinc-200">afilma.com</strong>. Growth Room does not collect or store payment card information.</li>
            <li>Access to purchased content is granted upon successful payment confirmation.</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to change our pricing at any time. Price changes do not affect purchases already completed.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">5. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We offer a <strong class="text-zinc-200">7-day money-back guarantee</strong> on all digital products sold through afilma.com,
            provided that:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>The refund request is submitted within 7 calendar days of the original purchase date.</li>
            <li>You have not consumed more than 20% of the course content (e.g., watched more than 20% of the videos).</li>
            <li>The request is made via email to <a href="mailto:support@growthroom.co" class="text-[#C9A44A] hover:text-white transition underline">support@growthroom.co</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Refunds for live coaching sessions or mastermind memberships are evaluated on a case-by-case basis.
            Approved refunds will be processed within 10 business days through the original payment method.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on this website and within our courses — including videos, text, graphics, logos,
            templates, and course materials — is the exclusive property of Growth Room and is protected by
            applicable copyright and intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Upon purchase, you are granted a <strong class="text-zinc-200">personal, non-transferable, non-exclusive license</strong> to
            access and use the purchased content for your own private, non-commercial purposes. You may not:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>Share, resell, sublicense, or redistribute any course content.</li>
            <li>Record, copy, or reproduce live sessions without prior written consent.</li>
            <li>Use our content to create competing products or services.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            Our courses and coaching sessions are educational in nature. Results vary based on individual
            effort, experience, market conditions, and other factors beyond our control.
            <strong class="text-zinc-200">Growth Room does not guarantee specific financial results</strong> from using our
            content or strategies. Any income figures mentioned are examples and not promises of typical results.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Our services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied,
            including but not limited to warranties of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, Growth Room shall not be liable for any
            indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of
            our services, including but not limited to loss of profits, data, or business opportunities.
            Our total liability for any claim shall not exceed the amount you paid for the relevant product
            or service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">9. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
            <li>Use our website or services for any unlawful purpose.</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of our systems.</li>
            <li>Share your account credentials with third parties.</li>
            <li>Post or transmit harmful, defamatory, or misleading content in any community space we operate.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">10. Third-Party Links and Platforms</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites, including afilma.com and social media
            platforms. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of any third-party
            site. Visiting third-party sites is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">11. Modifications to the Service</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of our services at any time
            with reasonable notice. We will not be liable to you or any third party for any such modification
            or discontinuation.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">12. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Brazil (for
            Brazilian customers, under the Consumer Defense Code — CDC) and the laws of the jurisdiction in
            which Growth Room is incorporated (for international customers), without regard to conflict of
            law principles. Any disputes shall be resolved in the competent courts of the applicable jurisdiction.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">13. Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms of Use at any time. We will notify users of material changes by
            updating the date at the top of this page. Continued use of our services after changes
            are posted constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-white">14. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us at:<br />
            <a href="mailto:support@growthroom.co" class="text-[#C9A44A] hover:text-white transition underline">support@growthroom.co</a>
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 border-t border-white/8 pt-8 text-xs text-zinc-600">
        <p>
          © {new Date().getFullYear()} Growth Room. All rights reserved. ·
          <a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:text-zinc-400 transition">Privacy Policy</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
